<li class='cover' id='bookCover_49123131'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/49123131-camino-winds"><img alt="Camino Winds (Camino Island, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1580242935l/49123131._SX98_.jpg" />
